        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3673112484" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6600879320658390927">Started out a little slow, but as new characters were added and others fleshed out, this became a compelling story about the underside of human nature in the Jim Crow South. Recommended for its seemingly honest portrayal of the vagaries of life during another era of American history.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


