              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6137926177736633787">Definitely engrossing, in the way that eccentric, wealthy, and largely unlikeable characters tend to be. The narration is suitably caustic, though a real affection for the Deep South is readily apparent.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


