<div id="review_3732123354" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3732123354" />
    <a title="Sue" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/2947947-sue"><img alt="Sue" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1517586546p2/2947947.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3732123354?book_show_action=true">Jan 22, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sue" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sue" href="/user/show/2947947-sue">Sue</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2947947-sue?shelf=family">family</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2947947-sue?shelf=read-in-2021">read-in-2021</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3732123354" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2939013699306017233">This book from Civil War historian Shelby Foote is pure Southern Gothic delight. <br/><br/>The story centers around 5 main characters, 4 of whom are truly awful people in a fictional town in Mississippi. The story spans across Spanish American war through WWI and into the Jazz Age and follows ill-fated love triangles (is love-quadrangle a thing?).<br/><br/>Loved every minute of this book.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

